data.description: Great opportunity for an entry level buyer or investor. Close drive to Tahoe Reno industrial park. Updated and upgraded, this 2 primary suite home is a unique and desirable floorplan, not usually found in this price range.  No HOA and a 2 car garage make this one of the best values in town.  See this property soon, before some else takes advantage of this opportunity.
